        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:10:08 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:10:08 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="SUSAN MONTOYA BRYAN, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/22/escape-from-killer-new-mexico-wildfire-was-absolute-sheer-terror-says-woman-who-fled-the-flames.webp" alt="Escape from killer New Mexico wildfire was 'absolute sheer terror,&#8217; says woman who fled the flames"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Escape from killer New Mexico wildfire was 'absolute sheer terror,&#8217; says woman who fled the flames</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Belinda Bukovitz was jolted into action by the sound of police outside her home shouting through a loudspeaker: “Go now, go now, go now!” Realizing this was not like other wildfires that had threatened her mountain village before, she, her husband, son and two cats bundled into three separate cars a
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/22/escape-from-killer-new-mexico-wildfire-was-absolute-sheer-terror-says-woman-who-fled-the-flames/"  >(SUSAN MONTOYA BRYAN, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:37:19 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:37:19 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Michael Bartiromo, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/21/climate-activists-call-out-taylor-swift-after-group-sprays-paint-on-private-jets.webp" alt="Climate activists call out Taylor Swift after group sprays paint on private jets"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Climate activists call out Taylor Swift after group sprays paint on private jets</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Climate activists belonging to a group known as Just Stop Oil sprayed paint on private jets at Stansted Airport in England on Thursday, with the group hinting that the airport was targeted because its “where Taylor Swift’s jet is parked.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/21/climate-activists-call-out-taylor-swift-after-group-sprays-paint-on-private-jets/"  >(Michael Bartiromo, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:14:32 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:14:32 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Anna Kutz, KRON4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/22/sex-testing-at-the-olympics-what-is-it-how-does-it-work.webp" alt="Sex testing at the Olympics: What is it? How does it work?"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sex testing at the Olympics: What is it? How does it work?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Though sex testing hasn't been mandatory for more than 20 years, athletes are still subject to evaluation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/22/sex-testing-at-the-olympics-what-is-it-how-does-it-work/"  >(Anna Kutz, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 04:07:12 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 04:07:12 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="CHRISTINA A. CASSIDY, Associated Press, PHL 17">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/22/gop-targets-a-biden-executive-order-on-voter-registration-ahead-of-the-fall-election.webp" alt="GOP targets a Biden executive order on voter registration ahead of the fall election"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">GOP targets a Biden executive order on voter registration ahead of the fall election</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      ATLANTA (AP) — Republicans and conservative activists have increasingly been targeting an executive order issued three years ago by the Biden administration that is intended to boost voter registration, claiming it's unconstitutional and an attempt to interfere in the November election.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/22/gop-targets-a-biden-executive-order-on-voter-registration-ahead-of-the-fall-election/"  >(CHRISTINA A. CASSIDY, Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:59:16 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:59:16 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="OLGA R. RODRIGUEZ, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/22/attacker-of-nancy-pelosis-husband-also-found-guilty-of-kidnapping-and-could-face-more-prison-time.webp" alt="Man who attacked Nancy Pelosi&#8217;s husband also found guilty of kidnapping and faces life in prison"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Man who attacked Nancy Pelosi&#8217;s husband also found guilty of kidnapping and faces life in prison</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAN FRANCISCO (AP) — A man sentenced to 30 years in federal prison in the attack against former House Speaker Nancy Pelosi’s husband was convicted Friday of aggravated kidnapping, a conviction that mandates life behind bars without the possibility of parole.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/22/attacker-of-nancy-pelosis-husband-also-found-guilty-of-kidnapping-and-could-face-more-prison-time/"  >(OLGA R. RODRIGUEZ, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:28:35 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:28:35 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Urja Sinha, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/21/major-lunar-standstill-to-light-up-stonehenge-on-summer-solstice.webp" alt="Major lunar standstill to light up Stonehenge on summer solstice"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Major lunar standstill to light up Stonehenge on summer solstice</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Scientists will be at Stonehenge throughout the “standstill season” to photograph moments when the moon is in alignment.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/21/major-lunar-standstill-to-light-up-stonehenge-on-summer-solstice/"  >(Urja Sinha, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:22:40 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:22:40 +0000">
