      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/21/shooting-at-arkansas-grocery-store-kills-2-wounds-8-others-police-say.webp" alt="Shooting at Arkansas grocery store kills 3, wounds 10 others, police say"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Shooting at Arkansas grocery store kills 3, wounds 10 others, police say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Arkansas State Police say two people were killed and eight wounded in a shooting that occurred Friday at a grocery store in south Arkansas.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/21/shooting-at-arkansas-grocery-store-kills-2-wounds-8-others-police-say/"  >(Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
