        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:46:55 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:46:55 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARCOS ALEMÁN, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/22/el-salvador-death-toll-rises-to-19-as-heavy-rains-continue.webp" alt="El Salvador death toll rises to 19 as heavy rains continue"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">El Salvador death toll rises to 19 as heavy rains continue</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAN SALVADOR, El Salvador (AP) — The torrential rains hitting El Salvador caused the deaths of another six people on Friday when two girls and four adults were killed after being buried in their homes. Wall collapses and landslides on the outskirts of the capital brought a total of 19 dead.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/22/el-salvador-death-toll-rises-to-19-as-heavy-rains-continue/"  >(MARCOS ALEMÁN, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 06:04:20 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 22 Jun 2024 06:04:20 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Moses Sawasawa And Monika Pronczuk, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/22/photos-in-the-spirit-of-perseverance-artists-flock-to-congos-biggest-dance-festival.webp" alt="AP PHOTOS: In the spirit of perseverance, artists flock to Congo's biggest dance festival"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">AP PHOTOS: In the spirit of perseverance, artists flock to Congo's biggest dance festival</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Goma dance festival, the largest dance festival in Congo, has taken place each year for the past seven years, despite ongoing attacks by rebel groups.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/22/photos-in-the-spirit-of-perseverance-artists-flock-to-congos-biggest-dance-festival/"  >(Moses Sawasawa And Monika Pronczuk, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 19 Jun 2024 16:36:57 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 19 Jun 2024 16:36:57 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/19/stonehenge-monument-painted-orange-climate-protesters-arrested.webp" alt="Stonehenge monument painted orange, climate protesters arrested"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Stonehenge monument painted orange, climate protesters arrested</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The latest act by Just Stop Oil was quickly condemned by Prime Minister Rishi Sunak as a “disgraceful act of vandalism.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/19/stonehenge-monument-painted-orange-climate-protesters-arrested/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:27:50 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:27:50 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Laura Kelly, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/21/israeli-prime-minister-criticizes-us-weapons.webp" alt="Netanyahu says US providing &#8216;trickle&#8217; of ammunition, weapons"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Netanyahu says US providing &#8216;trickle&#8217; of ammunition, weapons</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu is doubling down on criticisms that U.S. ammunition and weapons deliveries are arriving to Israel in a “trickle,” adding that he is airing private disagreements to force a change in the situation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/21/israeli-prime-minister-criticizes-us-weapons/"  >(Laura Kelly, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 11:13:29 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 11:13:29 -0400">
