           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former Hong Kong residents embrace UK politics amid lingering Beijing fears</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Hong Kong residents who moved to Britain under a visa program following political crackdowns back home have voiced their experience participating in British democracy.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/21/former-hong-kong-residents-embrace-uk-politics-lingering-beijing-fears/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
