  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/21/russia-open-dialogue-us-kremlin.webp" alt="Russia 'open to dialogue' with US: Kremlin"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Russia 'open to dialogue' with US: Kremlin</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A Kremlin spokesman said Russia is open to talks with the U.S., but only if Ukraine is included in the discussion. The U.S. says war negotiations are Ukraine&apos;s domain.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/21/russia-open-dialogue-us-kremlin/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
