        <a href="/tech/">Technology</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:21:11 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:21:11 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="SOPHIE AUSTIN, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/tech/2024/06/18/california-governor-wants-to-restrict-smartphone-usage-in-schools.webp" alt="California governor wants to restrict smartphone usage in schools"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">California governor wants to restrict smartphone usage in schools</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SACRAMENTO, Calif. (AP) — California Gov. Gavin Newsom announced Tuesday that he wants to restrict students' usage of smartphones during the school day, citing the mental health risks of social media. The announcement, which was first reported by Politico, comes a day after U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/18/california-governor-wants-to-restrict-smartphone-usage-in-schools/"  >(SOPHIE AUSTIN, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 11:45:46 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 21 Jun 2024 11:45:46 +0000">
