    <h3 itemprop="headline">Willie Mays almost got kicked out of high school while playing for the Birmingham Black Barons</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Willie Mays was just 16 years old when he went to play for the Birmingham Black Barons, beginning what would be a star-making turn as one of baseball's most iconic players.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/20/willie-mays-almost-got-kicked-out-of-high-school-while-playing-for-the-birmingham-black-barons/"  >(Drew Taylor, Fox 5)</a>
