    <p itemprop="text">
      Justin Lamkin gave Texas A&M a second straight sensational start, Caden Sorrell homered to break open the game and the Aggies beat Florida 6-0 to reach their first College World Series finals.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/22/texas-am-beats-florida-6-0-to-make-cws-finals-for-1st-time-as-gators-shut-out-1st-time-in-2-years/"  >(Eric Olson, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
